mage/f=auto,width=64/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2020/10/Micrograph-showing-cells-undergoing-metaphase-M-and-anaphase-A.png 64w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=96/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2020/10/Micrograph-showing-cells-undergoing-metaphase-M-and-anaphase-A.png 96w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=128/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2020/10/Micrograph-showing-cells-undergoing-metaphase-M-and-anaphase-A.png 128w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=256/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2020/10/Micrograph-showing-cells-undergoing-metaphase-M-and-anaphase-A.png 256w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=384/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2020/10/Micrograph-showing-cells-undergoing-metaphase-M-and-anaphase-A.png 384w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=640/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2020/10/Micrograph-showing-cells-undergoing-metaphase-M-and-anaphase-A.png 640w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=750/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2020/10/Micrograph-showing-cells-undergoing-metaphase-M-and-anaphase-A.png 750w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=828/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2020/10/Micrograph-showing-cells-undergoing-metaphase-M-and-anaphase-A.png 828w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=1080/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2020/10/Micrograph-showing-cells-undergoing-metaphase-M-and-anaphase-A.png 1080w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=1200/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2020/10/Micrograph-showing-cells-undergoing-metaphase-M-and-anaphase-A.png 1200w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=1920/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/2020/10/Micrograph-showing-cells-undergoing-metaphase-M-and-anaphase-A.png 1920w, https://cdn.savemyexams.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,width=2048/https://cdn.savemyexams.com/uploads/202